OL,7,FThe government is promising to give
OL,8,Fmore regions the chance to operate
OL,9,Fbuses similar to how they are managed
OL,10,Fin the capital, ITV News Political
OL,11,FCorrespondent Lucy McDaid reports
OL,13,FThe government has revealed where #1
OL,14,Fbillion in funding will go to deliver
OL,15,FLondon-style buses nationwide as part
OL,16,Fof a massive Budget boost.
