OL,7,FTransport Secretary Louise Haigh on
OL,8,FSunday confirmed #712 million in
OL,9,Ffunding for local authorities to
OL,10,Fimprove services, alongside a further
OL,11,F#243 million for bus operators.
OL,13,FAreas receiving an "unprecedented"
OL,14,Famount of funding include
OL,15,FPeterborough, the Isle of Wright,
OL,16,FTorbay, Cambridgeshire, Leicester and
OL,17,FTorbay.
