OL,7,FCombined authorities representing
OL,8,FSouth Yorkshire and Liverpool City
OL,9,Fregion will receive #17 million and
OL,10,Fnearly #21 million respectively.
OL,12,FA reformed allocation model has been
OL,13,Fbased on need ` for example an area's
OL,14,Flevels of deprivation and population `
OL,15,Finstead of making areas compete for
OL,16,Ffunding as in previous years.
OL,18,FMs Haigh said the investment would end
OL,19,F"complicated and inconsistent" funding
OL,20,Fmodels that have impacted passengers
OL,21,Ffor years.
