OL,4,Cbuses across the country with #1bn
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,F"Buses are the lifeblood of
OL,8,Fcommunities, but the system is
OL,9,Fbroken," she said.
OL,11,F"Too often, passengers are left
OL,12,Fwaiting hours for buses that don't
OL,13,Fturn up ` and some have been cut off
OL,14,Faltogether.
OL,16,F"That's why we're reforming funding to
OL,17,Fdeliver better buses across the
OL,18,Fcountry and end the postcode lottery
OL,19,Fof bus services."
