OL,3,CGovernment promises 'London-style'
OL,4,Cbuses across the country with #1bn
OL,5,Cboost
OL,7,FThe policy comes alongside the
OL,8,Fgovernment's recent decision to cap
OL,9,Ffares at a maximum of #3 during the
OL,10,Fbudget.
OL,12,FAn inflationary limit will also be set
OL,13,Fto ensure other fares are not
OL,14,Fautomatically increased to #3. The cap
OL,15,Fwill run until the end of 2025.
OL,17,FSingle bus fares in England have been
OL,18,Fcapped at #2 outside London, where
OL,19,Fthey are #1.75 per journey, for most
OL,20,Froutes since January 2023.
